snippet.textDisplay:
মিলন হবে কত দিনে

আমার মনের মানুষের সনে।।


চাতক প্রায় অহর্নিশি

চেয়ে আছি কালো শশী

হব বলে চরণ দাসী,

ও তা হয় না কপাল গুণে।।



মেঘের বিদ্যুৎ মেঘে যেমন

লুকালে না পায় অন্বেষণ,

কালারে হারায়ে তেমন

ঐ রূপ হেরি এ দর্পণে।।


যখন ও-রূপ স্মরণ হয়,

থাকে না লোকলজ্জার ভয়

লালন ফকির ভেবে বলে সদাই

ও প্রেম যে করে সেই জানে।।

snippet.textDisplay: Lalan was Bengali thats it. Clive partitioned Bangalis. Bengalis were a separate nation under Pals, Sens and so many more. Even if rest of history North and East had same rulers Bengalis are still distinct from any North Indian group today. Ashoka, Nandas, Shashanka all originated from Greater Bengal area comprising of modern day Bihar, Chattisgarh to Tripura, Chittagong. Buddha was from the Eastern India. Bengali has more Prakrit and Sanskrit than any North Indian language and Bengalis worship Bengali/Sanskrit irrespective of religion. Unlike Northies and Pakistanis, they are their own group also.
